<node CREATED="1437081206378" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_754383386" MODIFIED="1457520382025" TEXT="MeasureSpec can be in one of three modes:">
<node CREATED="1437081210136" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1789795595" MODIFIED="1457520382025" TEXT="UNSPECIFIED">
<node CREATED="1437081228299" ID="ID_719199951" MODIFIED="1437081232556" TEXT="used by a parent to determine the&#xa; desired dimension of a child view."/>
<node CREATED="1437081546916" ID="ID_1556763523" MODIFIED="1437081562286" TEXT="For example, a LinearLayout may call &#xa;measure() on its child with the height &#xa;set to UNSPECIFIED and a width of &#xa;EXACTLY 240 to find out how tall the &#xa;child view wants to be given a width&#xa; of 240 pixels."/>
</node>
